Nradio v0.1
Ncurses frontend (with playlist) for web radiostations.
Uses mpg123 and ogg123.

usage: nradio playlistfile

Navigation: j - down, k - up, enter - choose radiostation,
q - abort playing and return to playlist.

Example of .nrp (NRadio Playlist) file in directory.
It has simple structure:
---
Name in playlist0
URL0
Name in playlist1
URL1
Name in playlist2
URL2
...
---

